WEBVTT

01:30.840 --> 01:35.009
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:36.000 --> 01:39.289
[2005]

01:38.479 --> 01:39.729
Who would've thought

01:39.289 --> 01:41.600
[Certificate of Honor]

01:39.759 --> 01:41.500
the first place in this essay contest

01:41.500 --> 01:43.160
actually went to Xia Xiaolan?

01:43.710 --> 01:44.910
As if she deserves it.

01:48.430 --> 01:49.590
Are you blind?

02:07.480 --> 02:08.190
Stand up!

02:11.080 --> 02:13.710
-Good morning, teacher.
-Good morning, teacher.

02:13.710 --> 02:14.680
Good morning, students.

02:14.680 --> 02:15.610
Please sit down.

02:19.440 --> 02:20.750
Please take out your math textbooks.

02:20.750 --> 02:21.890
Let's begin today's lesson.

02:21.890 --> 02:23.190
Jealousy is a knife—

02:23.360 --> 02:24.890
sometimes it hurts others,

02:25.240 --> 02:27.710
and sometimes it hurts the one holding it.

02:28.180 --> 02:31.700
[Episode 18: The One Holding the Knife]

02:34.079 --> 02:34.750
Chen,

02:35.470 --> 02:36.800
the Asian Games is

02:36.800 --> 02:38.120
a huge opportunity for our brand!

02:38.120 --> 02:39.440
Right now, the biggest sporting event

02:39.230 --> 02:41.400
[Luna]

02:39.470 --> 02:40.590
our country can host

02:40.590 --> 02:41.520
is the Asian Games.

02:41.520 --> 02:42.860
[The Asian Games Torch Relay Begins Today]

02:41.810 --> 02:43.370
We won't be able to host the Olympics

02:42.860 --> 02:44.210
[Starting from the Himalayas,
Carrying the Light of the Games]

02:43.400 --> 02:43.960
until 2008,

02:43.960 --> 02:44.560
you know?

02:44.630 --> 02:46.000
Asian Games lottery tickets!

02:46.000 --> 02:47.310
Get your lottery tickets here, everyone!

02:47.310 --> 02:47.750
Two tickets.

02:47.750 --> 02:49.120
Sir, do you want two?

02:49.750 --> 02:50.810
Here, two tickets!

02:51.400 --> 02:53.120
Here, five tickets! Here!

02:53.120 --> 02:53.430
Three tickets!

02:53.430 --> 02:54.400
Let's support the Asian Games!

02:54.400 --> 02:55.960
Three tickets, alright!

02:56.520 --> 02:58.050
Sir, I won the second prize!

02:58.150 --> 02:59.280
I won!

02:59.310 --> 02:59.980
[Happy Home]

03:00.400 --> 03:00.960
Hello.

03:00.960 --> 03:02.490
Welcome to Happy Home Materials!

03:02.490 --> 03:03.240
Here, take a look.

03:03.240 --> 03:04.280
Right now, for in-store purchases...

03:04.280 --> 03:04.910
Hello.

03:05.030 --> 03:06.190
Customers who spend 999 yuan or more today

03:06.190 --> 03:07.950
can receive an Asian Games souvenir.

03:07.950 --> 03:09.550
[The Spirit of Asia; The 11th Asian Games]

03:15.750 --> 03:17.430
-Go China!
-Go China!

03:17.020 --> 03:23.620
♪ The spirit of Asia,
as one we will stand ♪

03:17.590 --> 03:18.960
-Go China!
-Go China!

03:19.190 --> 03:20.630
-Go China!
-Go China!

03:20.840 --> 03:22.400
-Go China!
-Go China!

03:22.590 --> 03:24.120
-Go China!
-Go China!

03:23.890 --> 03:31.180
♪ The spirit of Asia,
bring on all the joy ♪

03:24.360 --> 03:26.310
-Go China!
-Go China!

03:31.360 --> 03:38.010
♪ The spirit of Asia,
striving the best we can ♪

03:38.520 --> 03:45.650
♪ The spirit of Asia,
let's join hand in hand ♪

03:45.800 --> 03:52.540
♪ Asia will always be
the pride of all our lives ♪

03:51.630 --> 03:52.680
Take your time browsing.

03:52.680 --> 03:53.750
Feel free to try them on.

03:53.090 --> 04:00.130
♪ The pride of all our lives ♪

03:54.680 --> 03:55.710
Would you like to pair it with a bag?

03:55.710 --> 03:57.120
How is it? See anything you like?

03:57.120 --> 03:57.800
It matches your shoes—

03:57.800 --> 03:58.750
a perfect complement.

03:58.750 --> 03:59.520
Here, try it.

03:59.630 --> 04:00.310
You can try it on.

04:00.310 --> 04:02.040
The fitting room is over there.

04:02.190 --> 04:02.750
Okay.

04:03.840 --> 04:07.400
♪ The pride of all our lives ♪

04:06.630 --> 04:07.630
Mr. Chen, your business is really booming!

04:07.630 --> 04:08.560
Thank you, thank you.

04:08.560 --> 04:09.890
No problem. No problem.

04:10.670 --> 04:14.310
♪ The pride of all our lives ♪

04:11.360 --> 04:12.620
Is seven o'clock okay?

04:13.080 --> 04:14.840
I'll arrange it. I'll handle it.

04:14.840 --> 04:15.470
Don't mention it.

04:15.470 --> 04:16.360
Okay, okay.

04:22.040 --> 04:23.040
This collar here—

04:23.430 --> 04:24.480
make it a bit wider.

04:24.480 --> 04:25.310
Make it an off-the-shoulder style.

04:25.310 --> 04:25.800
Okay.

04:25.950 --> 04:26.680
It looks better that way.

04:26.680 --> 04:27.240
Chen,

04:27.560 --> 04:28.920
our branch stores are about to open.

04:28.920 --> 04:31.320
Why haven't we seen
any movement from Ji Ya?

04:31.430 --> 04:32.830
My friend at the Longcheng Garment Factory

04:32.830 --> 04:33.600
told me

04:33.830 --> 04:34.720
that Ji Ya has placed
a bulk order with them

04:34.720 --> 04:35.950
for ready-made clothes.

04:35.950 --> 04:37.560
The main production run was already done,

04:37.560 --> 04:38.120
but

04:38.380 --> 04:39.920
she wasn't satisfied with the buttons.

04:39.920 --> 04:41.159
They didn't meet her requirements.

04:41.159 --> 04:42.090
So Ji Ya has decided

04:42.090 --> 04:42.920
to order a batch of

04:42.920 --> 04:44.480
custom-made buttons overseas.

04:44.480 --> 04:46.700
So production is halted,
just waiting for the buttons.

04:46.700 --> 04:48.360
That level of perfectionism does sound

04:48.360 --> 04:49.800
very much like

04:49.800 --> 04:50.800
Ms. Ji Ya's style.

04:53.830 --> 04:55.630
From a designer's perspective,

04:55.750 --> 04:57.310
I actually envy her.

04:58.020 --> 04:58.950
She has deep enough pockets

04:58.950 --> 05:00.210
to pursue perfection.

05:00.460 --> 05:01.820
Pursuing perfection is great,

05:01.820 --> 05:03.410
but we have to consider
the domestic market,

05:03.410 --> 05:05.210
mass appeal, and popular taste.

05:05.430 --> 05:06.430
Spending that much

05:06.430 --> 05:07.430
on

05:07.430 --> 05:08.760
such a subtle detail...

05:09.040 --> 05:10.950
The customer is ultimately the one
who pays,

05:10.950 --> 05:12.950
and I don't think they'll pay for it.

05:13.320 --> 05:14.720
But Ji Ya should be ready soon.

05:14.720 --> 05:15.750
From what I've heard,

05:15.750 --> 05:17.270
Elegance's first batch of garments

05:17.270 --> 05:18.920
should be hitting the market soon.

05:18.920 --> 05:19.450
Alright.

05:19.640 --> 05:20.690
Let's not panic

05:20.720 --> 05:22.120
and stick to our own pace.

05:22.120 --> 05:23.000
We can start opening

05:23.000 --> 05:24.260
franchise stores now.

05:24.310 --> 05:25.920
How are things going with Wu Kaili?

05:25.920 --> 05:26.650
Don't worry.

05:26.720 --> 05:27.750
I've been maintaining my connections

05:27.750 --> 05:28.810
on Wu Kaili's side.

05:29.210 --> 05:30.000
This time, we're offering

05:30.000 --> 05:31.750
a generous and fair endorsement deal.

05:31.750 --> 05:32.950
She has no reason to refuse.

05:32.950 --> 05:33.510
Alright.

05:33.870 --> 05:35.830
Next, we should think about

05:35.920 --> 05:37.850
which time slots to buy for our ads.

05:40.280 --> 05:41.690
The dish is here.

05:41.720 --> 05:42.680
Enjoy your meal.

05:45.070 --> 05:46.360
Here's the dish.

05:46.630 --> 05:47.480
Thank you!

05:47.870 --> 05:48.600
Thanks, San!

05:49.510 --> 05:50.240
San,

05:50.270 --> 05:51.190
I think we should just

05:51.190 --> 05:52.720
invest in your restaurant.

05:53.240 --> 05:54.560
That would be wonderful.

05:54.560 --> 05:55.630
You're all big bosses,

05:55.630 --> 05:57.560
and I can just ride your coattails!

06:00.120 --> 06:01.870
After I close up tomorrow night,

06:01.870 --> 06:02.950
let's hit the boxing gym?

06:02.950 --> 06:03.630
Sure.

06:04.200 --> 06:04.600
Okay.

06:04.630 --> 06:05.560
Enjoy your food.

06:07.720 --> 06:08.390
Xia.

06:09.190 --> 06:11.520
I still know some people
at the TV stations

06:11.680 --> 06:13.110
in Shengcheng and Longcheng.

06:13.110 --> 06:14.310
How about I reach out
to my connections first?

06:14.310 --> 06:15.630
Local TV stations

06:15.630 --> 06:16.750
don't have enough reach.

06:16.750 --> 06:18.390
The goal of our advertising campaign

06:18.390 --> 06:19.040
is not only to expand

06:19.040 --> 06:20.180
our brand awareness—

06:20.180 --> 06:21.330
more importantly,

06:21.360 --> 06:22.930
it's to attract franchisees.

06:22.930 --> 06:24.160
We need to strive to expand Luna

06:24.160 --> 06:26.560
across the country as quickly as possible.

06:26.720 --> 06:29.320
So you mean Hua TV,
the national broadcaster?

06:31.790 --> 06:34.200
Would they air ads

06:34.240 --> 06:37.000
for a new private brand like ours?

06:37.630 --> 06:39.510
We're not exactly
a long-established brand.

06:39.510 --> 06:40.600
"Dear viewers,

06:40.950 --> 06:42.680
that concludes today's news."

06:43.360 --> 06:44.310
I think that time slot right there

06:44.310 --> 06:44.970
is perfect.

06:51.070 --> 06:52.120
This time slot?

06:54.070 --> 06:54.560
Well...

06:54.870 --> 06:55.330
Well...

06:55.360 --> 06:56.270
Aren't we getting

06:56.270 --> 06:58.010
a little ahead of ourselves here?

06:58.010 --> 06:59.070
Exactly, Xiaolan.

06:59.070 --> 07:00.180
My dear sister,

07:00.310 --> 07:01.360
you're really dreaming big.

07:01.360 --> 07:03.510
I don't think we can do that.

07:05.240 --> 07:05.770
Xiaolan,

07:06.310 --> 07:06.950
do you remember my mom's

07:06.950 --> 07:08.750
classmate, Ms. Zhan?

07:09.000 --> 07:10.220
You met her at the English competition.

07:10.220 --> 07:10.880
I remember.

07:11.040 --> 07:12.830
She seems to have connections at Hua TV.

07:12.830 --> 07:13.830
I'll ask her later

07:14.160 --> 07:15.870
and see if I can get an appointment
with the person in charge.

07:15.870 --> 07:17.750
Then we can talk in person
when we get back to Jingcheng.

07:17.750 --> 07:19.920
That seems like too much trouble
to put Ms. Zhan through.

07:19.920 --> 07:20.190
But

07:20.190 --> 07:21.870
I'm planning to go back to Jingcheng

07:21.870 --> 07:22.930
to see what I can do.

07:23.120 --> 07:24.000
Since we managed to

07:24.000 --> 07:25.430
get performers to wear our brand
at the gala before,

07:25.430 --> 07:26.190
we can definitely

07:26.190 --> 07:27.560
secure the ad slot too.

07:28.070 --> 07:29.310
Don't dismiss it just yet.

07:29.310 --> 07:30.640
Let's go back together.

07:31.390 --> 07:33.360
It's always good to have another option.

07:33.360 --> 07:33.920
Okay.

07:34.630 --> 07:35.310
Oh, Chen,

07:35.560 --> 07:36.830
alongside the TV ads,

07:36.920 --> 07:38.480
we also need to push hard
through print media

07:38.480 --> 07:39.480
to promote our new brand ambassador

07:39.480 --> 07:40.480
simultaneously.

07:40.510 --> 07:41.830
I think we need to find someone

07:41.830 --> 07:43.430
dedicated to handling that.

07:44.040 --> 07:45.500
Let's go with You Li, okay?

07:45.870 --> 07:46.390
Okay.

07:46.800 --> 07:47.510
I've been

07:47.510 --> 07:48.430
keeping an eye

07:48.430 --> 07:49.560
on her lately.

07:49.680 --> 07:50.830
At least from what I've seen so far,

07:50.830 --> 07:52.310
she's been doing solid work.

07:52.310 --> 07:53.560
So I'd like to give her another chance

07:53.560 --> 07:54.360
to grow.

07:55.159 --> 07:55.800
Xiaolan,

07:56.190 --> 07:57.990
I trust your judgment of people.

07:58.480 --> 07:59.480
I'm just puzzled—

07:59.659 --> 08:01.120
why was she

08:01.120 --> 08:02.680
warming up to me a while back?

08:02.680 --> 08:03.840
At that time, I think she really

08:03.840 --> 08:05.600
did seem interested in me.

08:05.800 --> 08:07.310
Could it be that she was moved

08:07.310 --> 08:08.750
by my irresistible charm?

08:08.750 --> 08:10.550
But she pulled back too quickly.

08:11.040 --> 08:12.270
Wei,

08:12.510 --> 08:13.630
don't flatter yourself.

08:13.630 --> 08:15.890
Can't you accept that maybe she realized

08:16.480 --> 08:17.070
she misjudged you

08:17.070 --> 08:18.980
and then suddenly came to her senses?

08:18.980 --> 08:19.360
Xiaolan,

08:19.360 --> 08:20.480
you used a word before

08:20.480 --> 08:21.630
to describe guys like him.

08:21.630 --> 08:22.630
What was it again?

08:23.240 --> 08:25.430
A narcissistic scumbag.

08:25.770 --> 08:26.800
-Scumbag.
-Scumbag.

08:26.800 --> 08:27.330
I... I...

08:27.800 --> 08:29.800
W-When did I ever act like a scumbag?

08:29.800 --> 08:31.530
You played with You Li's heart.

08:31.630 --> 08:32.390
I swear to God!

08:32.390 --> 08:33.510
I didn't do anything!

08:33.510 --> 08:34.120
Enough!

08:34.120 --> 08:35.780
Let's drink. Come on, cheers.

08:37.030 --> 08:41.080
[Jingcheng]

08:42.030 --> 08:42.840
Thank you, Auntie.

08:42.840 --> 08:44.100
Here, have some fruit.

08:48.080 --> 08:48.670
Xiaolan,

08:49.320 --> 08:51.030
don't blame me
for asking so many questions.

08:51.030 --> 08:53.080
You come straight to me wanting to meet

08:53.080 --> 08:54.600
the head of Hua TV's
advertising department.

08:54.600 --> 08:56.080
I have to ask what it's about

08:56.080 --> 08:57.910
so I know what to say to them, right?

08:57.910 --> 08:58.970
Of course, Auntie.

08:59.090 --> 09:00.890
We just want to get the TV station

09:00.910 --> 09:02.750
to advertise our clothing brand.

09:02.750 --> 09:03.360
Naturally,

09:03.360 --> 09:03.840
we'll pay

09:03.840 --> 09:05.500
the advertising fees in full.

09:05.510 --> 09:06.670
It's just that we want

09:06.670 --> 09:07.600
the slot right after

09:07.600 --> 09:08.730
the news broadcast.

09:08.840 --> 09:10.270
We don't know if there's an opening,

09:10.270 --> 09:11.360
so we want to talk to the person in charge

09:11.360 --> 09:12.080
directly.

09:13.770 --> 09:14.770
Right off the bat,

09:14.910 --> 09:16.000
you're aiming for Hua TV

09:16.000 --> 09:17.390
and even the post-news slot?

09:17.390 --> 09:18.200
Xiaolan, has your business

09:18.200 --> 09:19.390
grown that big?

09:22.790 --> 09:24.030
Do you remember Auntie Zhan
from the English competition

09:24.030 --> 09:25.070
back then?

09:25.360 --> 09:26.630
She works at Hua TV.

09:27.390 --> 09:28.790
I'll have her ask around.

09:28.840 --> 09:30.200
Okay. Thank you, Auntie.

09:30.200 --> 09:31.130
Don't thank me just yet.

09:31.130 --> 09:33.000
We still need to
give her a heads-up first.

09:33.000 --> 09:33.960
We still don't know

09:33.960 --> 09:34.960
whether she'll be able to help,

09:34.960 --> 09:35.360
right?

09:35.670 --> 09:36.530
It's okay, Mom.

09:36.630 --> 09:37.550
Xiaolan has also reached out

09:37.550 --> 09:38.420
through the magazine agency.

09:38.420 --> 09:39.390
We're working on both fronts.

09:39.390 --> 09:39.920
Alright.

09:40.150 --> 09:41.750
Sorry to trouble you, Auntie.

09:41.750 --> 09:43.870
We're family. No need to be so polite.

09:44.320 --> 09:45.600
Stay for dinner tonight.

09:45.600 --> 09:46.360
I won't hear otherwise.

09:46.150 --> 09:47.980
[Shengcheng Commercial Bank]

09:50.840 --> 09:51.770
Comrade Liu Fen,

09:52.030 --> 09:53.210
here is your freshly issued passbook.

09:53.210 --> 09:53.510
Okay.

09:53.510 --> 09:54.080
Keep it safe.

09:54.080 --> 09:54.380
Thank you.

09:54.380 --> 09:56.110
It's a bit chaotic around here.

09:59.150 --> 09:59.630
Fen!

09:59.810 --> 10:00.510
Are you done with your business?

10:00.510 --> 10:01.150
Yeah.

10:02.750 --> 10:04.790
This is Chief Ma from the police station.

10:04.790 --> 10:05.320
Chief Ma, hello.

10:05.320 --> 10:06.150
Hello, nice to meet you.

10:06.150 --> 10:06.750
Hello, nice to meet you.

10:06.750 --> 10:08.150
Comrade Liu Fen's shop

10:08.170 --> 10:10.100
happens to be in our jurisdiction.

10:10.240 --> 10:11.000
She's a woman on her own,

10:11.000 --> 10:12.390
coming to the bank for business often.

10:12.390 --> 10:14.520
I was worried something might happen,

10:14.750 --> 10:15.790
so I came along.

10:16.510 --> 10:17.200
Thank you.

10:18.120 --> 10:19.750
I'm usually busy with work

10:19.910 --> 10:20.960
and lots of meetings too.

10:20.960 --> 10:22.240
Thanks for looking out for her.

10:22.240 --> 10:24.100
It's my duty. Serving the people.

10:24.550 --> 10:25.670
It's already noon.

10:26.200 --> 10:27.480
Let's grab lunch together.

10:27.480 --> 10:27.790
Yeah.

10:27.790 --> 10:28.480
-Why not join us?
-Sure.

10:28.480 --> 10:29.870
I'll pass. I still have work
at the station.

10:29.870 --> 10:30.870
Come on, just a quick meal.

10:30.870 --> 10:32.070
No, really, I'm busy.

10:32.150 --> 10:33.240
Next time. Next time.

10:33.240 --> 10:34.040
Then we'll...

10:34.320 --> 10:35.240
We'll get going.

10:35.240 --> 10:35.670
Okay.

10:35.670 --> 10:36.360
Next time, you have to join us, okay?

10:36.360 --> 10:36.720
Sure.

10:36.750 --> 10:37.120
Okay.

10:37.440 --> 10:38.030
Goodbye.

10:38.480 --> 10:38.840
Bye.

10:41.600 --> 10:42.030
Goodbye.

10:42.030 --> 10:42.750
Bye. Bye.

10:52.840 --> 10:54.100
You can tell at a glance

10:54.200 --> 10:55.800
that Chief Ma is a decent man.

10:58.790 --> 10:59.910
Ma is very nice.

11:00.550 --> 11:02.720
Once, when I went to deposit money,

11:03.190 --> 11:04.320
a thief targeted me.

11:04.670 --> 11:06.480
Chief Ma helped me out.

11:07.080 --> 11:08.150
Since then,

11:08.510 --> 11:10.110
he's been looking out for me.

11:12.550 --> 11:14.350
Then we really should thank him.

11:14.750 --> 11:15.600
How about this?

11:15.600 --> 11:16.600
When we have time,

11:16.600 --> 11:18.000
I'll treat him to dinner.

11:19.120 --> 11:21.250
That... That's not really necessary.

11:21.360 --> 11:22.890
I gave him some specialties

11:23.270 --> 11:24.870
I brought back

11:25.240 --> 11:26.440
from my hometown.

11:28.630 --> 11:30.560
Actually, I know how Chief Ma feels

11:30.840 --> 11:31.510
about me.

11:32.680 --> 11:35.160
I made it clear
I didn't feel the same way.

11:36.360 --> 11:37.790
Ma is quite gracious.

11:38.790 --> 11:39.790
He never

11:40.390 --> 11:42.120
brought it up again after that.

11:44.120 --> 11:45.320
Looks like I have

11:45.480 --> 11:46.540
quite a few rivals.

11:49.150 --> 11:50.590
It just shows that the woman I like

11:50.590 --> 11:51.850
is truly outstanding.

11:54.630 --> 11:55.200
Fen,

11:56.030 --> 11:56.670
I know.

11:57.240 --> 11:58.270
You don't

11:58.630 --> 11:59.760
want to rush things.

12:00.630 --> 12:01.510
It's okay.

12:02.040 --> 12:03.240
I don't mind waiting.

12:03.510 --> 12:04.570
We can take it slow.

12:13.610 --> 12:14.670
You mentioned earlier

12:14.670 --> 12:16.790
that you ran into a thief.

12:17.000 --> 12:18.530
Does Xiaolan know about it?

12:19.240 --> 12:20.720
Xiaolan has so much on her plate.

12:20.720 --> 12:21.520
She's so busy.

12:21.750 --> 12:22.750
I didn't tell her.

12:24.600 --> 12:25.330
Makes sense.

12:26.240 --> 12:27.100
If you told her,

12:27.320 --> 12:28.510
she'd only worry.

12:29.600 --> 12:31.400
You really think of everything.

12:33.480 --> 12:35.410
Xiaolan certainly never imagined it.

12:35.410 --> 12:36.050
Back then,

12:36.080 --> 12:37.340
she took her mother out

12:37.390 --> 12:38.590
to run a street stall,

12:38.750 --> 12:40.270
striving and fighting to build

12:40.270 --> 12:42.070
a better life for the two of them,

12:42.550 --> 12:43.390
while her mom handled things

12:43.390 --> 12:44.150
so well

12:44.780 --> 12:45.900
and grew so much.

12:46.470 --> 12:47.800
It's truly impressive.

12:51.270 --> 12:55.390
♪ A cool breeze drifts softly
through my coat ♪

12:56.080 --> 12:59.530
♪ Summer slips away without a sound ♪

13:00.730 --> 13:05.280
♪ The days rush by,
stirring waves of emotion ♪

13:05.590 --> 13:11.870
♪ I miss that moment, bright with color ♪

13:08.870 --> 13:10.470
Who is this beautiful lady?

13:13.840 --> 13:14.510
Auntie?

13:14.600 --> 13:15.510
Xiaolan!

13:15.750 --> 13:19.810
♪ A gentle breeze
carries you into my heart ♪

13:16.510 --> 13:17.270
My Xiaolan,

13:17.270 --> 13:19.120
it's been so long since I last saw you!

13:19.120 --> 13:20.390
Auntie, you're getting
younger and younger.

13:20.390 --> 13:21.240
You haven't changed a bit.

13:20.550 --> 13:24.000
♪ In that instant,
you changed my whole life ♪

13:21.320 --> 13:22.000
Not at all!

13:22.000 --> 13:24.130
You're the one who's gotten prettier!

13:24.440 --> 13:24.870
Come on, sit.

13:24.870 --> 13:25.910
Why have you gotten so thin, child?

13:25.390 --> 13:29.250
♪ All the love I've given
can't be measured ♪

13:25.910 --> 13:26.840
No, I haven't. Sit.

13:26.840 --> 13:28.030
Come on, let's sit together.

13:28.030 --> 13:28.690
Okay, okay.

13:28.910 --> 13:31.150
Let me take a good look at you.

13:30.030 --> 13:36.770
♪ And now, I no longer fear
the wind and rain ♪

13:31.600 --> 13:32.840
It's been so long.

13:33.510 --> 13:35.200
Auntie, that perm looks great on you.

13:35.200 --> 13:35.670
Really? Does it?

13:35.670 --> 13:36.270
Very nice.

13:36.390 --> 13:38.520
Just trying to keep up with the trends!

13:38.670 --> 13:39.270
Look at me—

13:39.440 --> 13:40.480
how's my lipstick?

13:39.700 --> 13:44.130
♪ Blow, blow, let the wind blow ♪

13:40.870 --> 13:42.120
It's the most popular shade
in Jingcheng right now.

13:42.120 --> 13:42.480
It looks great.

13:42.480 --> 13:43.960
I'll get you one next time.

13:43.960 --> 13:45.120
Okay, thank you, Auntie.

13:44.150 --> 13:49.560
♪ Wipe away the glistening tears
in your eyes ♪

13:45.910 --> 13:47.770
Did you come back alone this time?

13:47.870 --> 13:48.440
No.

13:48.600 --> 13:50.130
I came back with Zhou Cheng.

13:50.440 --> 13:51.040
Oh, right.

13:51.120 --> 13:51.630
This is a bag of

13:51.630 --> 13:52.740
the soup ingredients

13:52.740 --> 13:54.090
that Uncle mentioned you love.

13:54.090 --> 13:55.750
So I brought some back for you.

13:55.750 --> 13:57.870
Look at this big bag—so heavy!

13:57.960 --> 14:00.360
It's not heavy
with two people carrying it.

14:00.360 --> 14:01.720
How is Tao recently?

14:01.750 --> 14:02.950
Is he adjusting well?

14:03.270 --> 14:05.470
I don't need to worry about his studies.

14:05.790 --> 14:06.790
It's just that...

14:07.520 --> 14:08.640
I'm hoping to

14:08.670 --> 14:09.750
get things settled

14:09.750 --> 14:11.410
before he starts high school.

14:12.960 --> 14:14.750
I have an appointment this afternoon

14:14.750 --> 14:15.720
with someone from the TV station

14:15.720 --> 14:17.380
to discuss an advertisement.

14:17.510 --> 14:19.120
If the ad deal works out,

14:19.270 --> 14:20.720
along with the Luna franchise fees

14:20.720 --> 14:21.690
and the dividends later,

14:21.690 --> 14:23.120
we should be able to save enough money.

14:23.120 --> 14:24.030
After we save enough,

14:24.030 --> 14:25.810
we can buy land and build a house.

14:25.810 --> 14:26.530
By then,

14:26.550 --> 14:28.200
we can transfer
Tao's household registration here.

14:28.200 --> 14:28.660
Auntie,

14:28.750 --> 14:30.480
just give me a little more time.

14:31.320 --> 14:32.960
I'm not rushing you.

14:32.960 --> 14:34.560
You've already done so well.

14:34.910 --> 14:35.840
I know.

14:36.240 --> 14:36.910
Auntie,

14:37.320 --> 14:39.080
when I was at my lowest,

14:39.320 --> 14:39.920
it was you,

14:40.150 --> 14:41.200
Uncle, and Tao

14:41.200 --> 14:42.200
who gave us a home.

14:42.790 --> 14:43.440
Now that

14:43.840 --> 14:44.910
I have the means,

14:45.360 --> 14:46.870
I want to give you a home too.

14:46.870 --> 14:47.930
The best home I can.

14:49.390 --> 14:50.200
Silly child.

14:53.050 --> 14:54.180
Hearing you say that

14:54.200 --> 14:55.390
is enough for me.

14:56.960 --> 14:58.550
Alright, alright, Auntie. It's okay.

14:58.550 --> 15:00.360
Our Xiaolan is truly capable!

15:07.510 --> 15:09.240
Alright, stop trying to fix it.

15:09.390 --> 15:10.660
Let your dad fix it when he gets back.

15:10.660 --> 15:11.300
It's fine.

15:12.030 --> 15:13.290
Here, have some fruit.

15:13.510 --> 15:15.170
The cantaloupe is very sweet.

15:16.400 --> 15:16.790
Mom.

15:17.600 --> 15:18.440
Who did Auntie Zhan introduce

15:18.440 --> 15:19.360
to Xiaolan?

15:19.790 --> 15:20.720
Will it work out?

15:22.390 --> 15:23.080
She said it's the director

15:23.080 --> 15:25.240
of the TV station's
advertising department,

15:25.240 --> 15:26.080
surname Min.

15:26.550 --> 15:27.810
He's in charge of this.

15:29.460 --> 15:30.260
Director Min.

15:32.640 --> 15:33.770
Is it a man or a woman?

15:36.670 --> 15:37.510
A man.

15:38.440 --> 15:40.640
Look at you, that's all you think about.

15:41.150 --> 15:42.550
I'm not trying to nag you,

15:43.180 --> 15:44.750
but from Yunan to Jingcheng

15:44.780 --> 15:46.000
and then to Shengcheng,

15:46.000 --> 15:46.790
you've been following Xiaolan

15:46.790 --> 15:47.790
like a lost puppy.

15:48.870 --> 15:49.940
Be honest with me.

15:50.510 --> 15:51.320
What exactly are your intentions

15:51.320 --> 15:52.270
toward Xiaolan?

15:55.960 --> 15:56.820
I'm asking you.

15:57.320 --> 15:57.720
I fixed it!

15:57.720 --> 15:59.120
Turn it down. It's too loud.

15:59.120 --> 16:00.320
Isn't it good as new?

16:00.670 --> 16:02.200
I was asking you a question.

16:03.480 --> 16:04.010
Alright.

16:04.030 --> 16:04.600
I'm heading out.

16:04.600 --> 16:05.200
I still have things to attend to.

16:05.200 --> 16:06.320
Where are you going?

16:06.320 --> 16:07.590
To... pick up Xiaolan.

16:07.910 --> 16:09.030
Go then.

16:10.690 --> 16:11.670
When will you ever bring Xiaolan home

16:11.670 --> 16:13.710
as my daughter-in-law?

16:14.630 --> 16:15.790
Has Section Chief Zhan

16:15.790 --> 16:16.910
mentioned our station's situation

16:16.910 --> 16:18.000
to you beforehand?

16:18.390 --> 16:19.440
I asked Auntie Zhan

16:19.440 --> 16:20.570
about it in advance.

16:20.790 --> 16:21.870
She said

16:21.870 --> 16:24.030
some of the ad slots
were available for purchase,

16:24.030 --> 16:25.600
so I came to try my luck.

16:26.720 --> 16:27.600
Try your luck?

16:29.480 --> 16:31.360
This has nothing to do with luck.

16:31.630 --> 16:32.910
I'll be straight with you—

16:32.910 --> 16:34.910
yes, advertising slots can be purchased,

16:34.910 --> 16:36.600
but the content must be reviewed.

16:36.600 --> 16:37.150
However,

16:37.240 --> 16:39.510
we've never aired a clothing brand before.

16:39.510 --> 16:40.600
And different time slots

16:40.600 --> 16:41.930
have different prices.

16:43.150 --> 16:45.390
Which time slot are you looking to buy?

16:47.200 --> 16:47.730
Alright.

16:48.030 --> 16:49.030
Since you're being direct,

16:49.030 --> 16:50.480
I won't beat around the bush either.

16:50.480 --> 16:51.240
We want the slot

16:51.240 --> 16:52.960
immediately following the news broadcast.

16:52.960 --> 16:54.220
Please give us a quote.

16:57.600 --> 16:59.440
The slot after the news?

17:00.360 --> 17:01.670
That time usually features ads

17:01.670 --> 17:02.790
for bicycles,

17:02.870 --> 17:04.400
watches, and electronics.

17:05.109 --> 17:07.109
Do you know how big those brands are?

17:08.790 --> 17:09.790
You name the price,

17:09.790 --> 17:10.680
and I'll pay.

17:10.790 --> 17:11.910
As long as the ad passes review,

17:11.910 --> 17:12.950
we have a deal.

17:20.880 --> 17:22.270
The closer to the news broadcast,

17:22.270 --> 17:23.470
the higher the price.

17:26.160 --> 17:26.790
Ms. Xia,

17:27.440 --> 17:29.240
which specific slot do you want?

17:30.240 --> 17:31.480
The very first one,

17:31.480 --> 17:32.680
right after the news.

17:37.830 --> 17:38.510
Ms. Xia.

17:40.240 --> 17:42.060
Looks like the meeting went well.

17:42.060 --> 17:42.920
When did you get here?

17:42.920 --> 17:43.550
Just now.

17:43.960 --> 17:44.720
How did it go?

17:46.750 --> 17:47.410
Zhou Cheng,

17:47.910 --> 17:48.610
everyone else thinks

17:48.610 --> 17:50.210
wanting that ad slot

17:50.240 --> 17:51.240
is a pipe dream.

17:51.790 --> 17:53.590
Only you believe I can pull it off.

17:53.590 --> 17:55.240
It's not that I think you can pull it off,

17:55.240 --> 17:56.900
but I know that no matter what,

17:57.000 --> 17:58.200
you will give it a try.

17:58.240 --> 17:58.880
Instead of talking you out of it,

17:58.880 --> 17:59.720
I might as well think about

17:59.720 --> 18:00.720
how I can help you.

18:01.240 --> 18:02.310
But I didn't expect

18:02.310 --> 18:04.640
the advertising fee to be this expensive.

18:05.680 --> 18:06.740
It costs a million.

18:08.200 --> 18:08.790
How much?

18:09.400 --> 18:10.400
A million?

18:14.310 --> 18:15.110
Then how about

18:15.640 --> 18:17.400
we s-s-switch to a different time slot?

18:17.400 --> 18:18.350
No way.

18:18.680 --> 18:20.190
I've already put it out there.

18:20.190 --> 18:21.630
I'm set on that time slot.

18:22.750 --> 18:23.350
It's fine.

18:23.720 --> 18:24.960
Let's shoot the ad first

18:24.960 --> 18:26.690
and figure out the money later.

18:27.720 --> 18:28.750
Ms. Xia, I knew you

18:28.920 --> 18:30.320
wouldn't give up easily.

18:34.650 --> 18:36.540
[A page from Chen Xiliang:
Urgent, return immediately.]

18:36.440 --> 18:37.500
It's Chen Xiliang.

18:38.030 --> 18:38.880
Something might have happened.

18:38.880 --> 18:40.140
Let's go back quickly.

18:40.240 --> 18:40.830
Let's go.

18:41.030 --> 18:41.590
Okay.

18:44.110 --> 18:45.240
The venue and crew

18:45.240 --> 18:46.160
are ready,

18:46.270 --> 18:47.790
and we're scheduled to
start shooting tomorrow.

18:47.790 --> 18:49.070
The director is already at the hotel,

18:49.070 --> 18:49.720
on standby.

18:49.720 --> 18:51.240
Then, out of the blue,
Wu Kaili suddenly told me

18:51.240 --> 18:52.300
she wasn't coming.

18:52.360 --> 18:53.690
She says she'll pay the penalty.

18:53.690 --> 18:54.550
What use is that penalty

18:54.550 --> 18:55.400
if she's not coming?

18:55.400 --> 18:57.200
The whole crew is waiting to shoot.

18:57.200 --> 18:58.000
Has her side given

18:58.000 --> 18:59.000
any explanation?

18:59.400 --> 19:00.790
Her manager won't see me.

19:00.790 --> 19:03.440
They said they'll just follow
the penalty clause.

19:03.440 --> 19:05.500
She's probably found a better offer.

19:05.590 --> 19:07.190
T-Then what should we do now?

19:07.310 --> 19:08.370
Find someone else.

19:08.720 --> 19:09.830
The TV station wants the final footage

19:09.830 --> 19:10.550
by the 26th.

19:10.590 --> 19:11.400
Go and contact

19:11.400 --> 19:13.000
every female star you can reach.

19:13.000 --> 19:13.920
I'll check with Wu Kaili's side

19:13.920 --> 19:15.180
to see what's going on.

19:16.310 --> 19:17.160
Time is so tight.

19:17.160 --> 19:19.160
Where am I supposed to find someone?

19:31.790 --> 19:34.000
There's a brand called "Elegance."

19:34.180 --> 19:35.780
Have you heard of it, Ms. Xia?

19:37.200 --> 19:37.920
Elegance?

19:38.550 --> 19:40.310
So it was Ji Ya who poached her.

19:40.920 --> 19:42.440
There're plenty of singers in Gangdao

19:42.440 --> 19:43.590
more famous than Wu Kaili.

19:43.590 --> 19:44.250
She did this

19:44.440 --> 19:45.970
purely to get under my skin.

19:46.590 --> 19:47.350
Even someone like Wu Kaili

19:47.350 --> 19:48.690
would back out on you like that?

19:48.690 --> 19:49.440
Don't worry, Ms. Xia.

19:49.440 --> 19:50.900
I'll definitely help you.

19:50.960 --> 19:52.000
Why don't I ask her out for coffee

19:52.000 --> 19:52.750
so we can talk it through?

19:52.750 --> 19:53.350
No need.

19:53.840 --> 19:55.330
Even if she came crawling back right now,

19:55.330 --> 19:56.730
I wouldn't use her again.

19:57.070 --> 19:57.590
Mr. Du,

19:57.920 --> 19:59.590
you did me a favor this time.

19:59.790 --> 20:01.240
About you telling Xia Dajun

20:01.240 --> 20:02.900
about my shops in Shengcheng—

20:03.340 --> 20:04.470
I'll let that slide.

20:04.720 --> 20:05.200
Thanks.

20:05.550 --> 20:06.440
No, I...

20:08.960 --> 20:09.590
What?

20:10.240 --> 20:11.370
You upset her again?

20:12.510 --> 20:13.160
Xia Dajun

20:13.360 --> 20:14.780
really went to see Xia Xiaolan?

20:14.780 --> 20:16.540
Wasn't it you who told him?

20:17.070 --> 20:18.600
You sure acted fast on that.

20:18.720 --> 20:19.270
Go check

20:19.270 --> 20:20.590
what Xia Dajun is doing in Shengcheng.

20:20.590 --> 20:22.590
Okay, okay, I'll go check right now.

20:39.420 --> 20:40.710
[Director: Zhang Guangliang;
Starring: Teresa Li]

20:44.060 --> 20:44.740
[Millennium Icon Teresa Li—
China's International Star]

20:45.310 --> 20:46.170
[Chinese Actress Teresa Li Lights Up
the Serrano International Film Festival]

20:51.830 --> 20:52.310
Ms. Xia,

20:52.310 --> 20:52.790
aren't we leaving?

20:52.790 --> 20:53.920
Wait for me a moment.

20:55.400 --> 20:56.110
Andy?

20:56.510 --> 20:58.030
No "Andy" will work—

20:58.110 --> 20:59.520
we're a women's clothing brand!

20:59.520 --> 21:00.350
Keep looking!

21:00.590 --> 21:02.250
Alright, alright, thank you.

21:06.310 --> 21:07.030
Du Zhaohui!

21:10.440 --> 21:12.300
I need to borrow your brick phone.

21:24.550 --> 21:25.110
Hello?

21:25.550 --> 21:26.160
Xia.

21:26.510 --> 21:27.440
Check

21:27.440 --> 21:28.830
the earliest flight from Hushi

21:28.830 --> 21:29.960
to Shengcheng tomorrow.

21:29.960 --> 21:31.020
Contact Teresa Li.

21:31.110 --> 21:31.880
Teresa Li?

21:32.790 --> 21:34.030
She is pretty,

21:34.070 --> 21:35.520
but compared to Wu Kaili,

21:35.550 --> 21:37.080
isn't she much less famous?

21:37.170 --> 21:37.970
Stop arguing.

21:38.070 --> 21:38.880
Listen to me on this.

21:38.880 --> 21:39.790
In a couple of years, she'll be so famous

21:39.790 --> 21:40.960
you won't be able to afford her.

21:40.960 --> 21:41.750
Okay, okay.

21:41.750 --> 21:42.400
I got it.

21:46.480 --> 21:47.000
Thanks.

22:04.640 --> 22:05.770
Another emergency,

22:05.840 --> 22:07.400
so I used a cheat code again—

22:08.250 --> 22:09.590
drawing on Teresa Li's future fame

22:09.590 --> 22:10.520
to benefit Luna.

22:11.290 --> 22:12.620
I don't know if this will

22:12.640 --> 22:14.510
accelerate the countdown to my departure

22:14.510 --> 22:16.310
and muddle my memories further.

22:17.810 --> 22:19.610
As soon as I save enough money,

22:19.640 --> 22:21.900
I must withdraw from Luna's operations.

22:30.200 --> 22:32.200
Good thing you suggested Teresa Li.

22:32.450 --> 22:34.000
I reached out to everyone
I could think of,

22:34.000 --> 22:35.070
but no one agreed.

22:37.000 --> 22:39.440
Either they felt
the schedule was too tight,

22:39.440 --> 22:41.900
or they worried about complicated approval

22:41.920 --> 22:43.590
at their workplaces.

22:44.030 --> 22:45.160
Some were concerned

22:45.160 --> 22:47.030
that a commercial might
reflect badly on them

22:47.030 --> 22:49.310
and invite gossip from their colleagues.

22:49.310 --> 22:50.110
Only she—

22:50.880 --> 22:52.750
the moment I brought it up,
she immediately agreed.

22:52.750 --> 22:54.310
With that kind of personality—

22:54.310 --> 22:55.440
bold and ambitious—

22:55.960 --> 22:57.830
she'll definitely be famous one day.

22:57.830 --> 22:59.560
Xia, you have an eye for talent.

23:02.000 --> 23:02.830
Very good!

23:06.270 --> 23:06.800
Mr. Chen.

23:07.160 --> 23:07.880
Ms. Li.

23:09.830 --> 23:10.690
You're Ms. Xia?

23:13.030 --> 23:15.350
I didn't expect you to be
so young and beautiful.

23:15.350 --> 23:17.150
You should film the ad yourself.

23:17.640 --> 23:18.900
You flatter me, Ms. Li.

23:18.940 --> 23:20.410
Not everyone can act.

23:20.440 --> 23:21.510
My ambition lies elsewhere.

23:21.510 --> 23:22.910
I'll pass on filming ads.

23:24.200 --> 23:25.600
Thank you so much, Ms. Li,

23:25.720 --> 23:27.380
for saving Luna from a crisis.

23:28.440 --> 23:30.070
No need to be so formal, Mr. Chen.

23:30.070 --> 23:31.440
When the ad airs on TV,

23:31.640 --> 23:33.560
my face will be on it every day.

23:33.840 --> 23:34.760
It's a win-win,

23:35.030 --> 23:35.510
right?

23:36.750 --> 23:37.880
Ms. Li, I didn't expect you

23:37.880 --> 23:39.000
to be not only beautiful

23:39.000 --> 23:39.800
but also loyal

23:40.110 --> 23:41.040
and farsighted.

23:42.790 --> 23:43.350
Teresa,

23:43.590 --> 23:45.250
we're ready for the next shot.

23:45.550 --> 23:46.070
Coming.

23:46.200 --> 23:47.200
I'll go shoot now.

23:47.440 --> 23:48.400
I'll walk you over.

23:48.400 --> 23:48.920
Okay.

24:03.000 --> 24:05.130
She's poached your brand ambassador?

24:05.310 --> 24:06.640
Ji Ya is going to shoot a commercial too?

24:06.640 --> 24:08.160
Judging by Director Min's tone,

24:08.160 --> 24:09.070
Ji Ya probably doesn't

24:09.070 --> 24:10.600
plan to run TV commercials.

24:10.960 --> 24:12.640
At least not on Hua TV.

24:13.160 --> 24:15.030
But if we're talking about spending big,

24:15.030 --> 24:15.960
we might not

24:15.960 --> 24:17.760
have as much capital as she does.

24:19.350 --> 24:20.000
No.

24:20.570 --> 24:21.660
I need to secure

24:21.680 --> 24:22.750
that ad slot quickly.

24:22.750 --> 24:24.280
I can't let her beat us to it.

24:25.640 --> 24:27.400
Don't push yourself so hard.

24:28.030 --> 24:29.490
Life moves at its own pace,

24:29.830 --> 24:31.510
and so can your career.

24:33.680 --> 24:34.480
But...

24:34.830 --> 24:36.400
I don't have much time left.

24:39.050 --> 24:40.890
What do you mean?

24:44.750 --> 24:46.110
Property prices are rising

24:46.110 --> 24:47.270
so much faster

24:47.270 --> 24:48.270
than I can save up.

24:48.640 --> 24:50.440
This wretched real estate market.

24:50.440 --> 24:52.480
If I don't save enough to get in the game,

24:52.480 --> 24:54.200
I might be shut out completely.

24:54.200 --> 24:55.350
Tao is still waiting for me
to build a house,

24:55.350 --> 24:58.270
transfer his household registration to
Jingcheng, and send him to school there.

24:58.270 --> 25:00.030
You can't keep
putting everyone else's burdens

25:00.030 --> 25:01.630
on your own shoulders, okay?

25:02.070 --> 25:02.750
You can't just

25:02.750 --> 25:03.830
arrange everyone's

25:03.830 --> 25:05.160
future for them, right?

25:06.000 --> 25:07.070
If I leave,

25:08.030 --> 25:09.960
you'll be the one
whose life I have no clue

25:09.960 --> 25:11.030
how to arrange.

25:23.790 --> 25:25.050
Editor-in-Chief Cui,

25:25.110 --> 25:26.200
didn't we agree

25:26.200 --> 25:27.550
that the second half of the month's cover

25:27.550 --> 25:28.680
was reserved for us?

25:31.160 --> 25:32.020
A fashion show?

25:32.670 --> 25:33.150
Yes.

25:33.590 --> 25:35.510
I know. It's just getting a few people

25:35.510 --> 25:36.680
to walk the runway.

25:36.680 --> 25:38.110
It's just a gimmick.

25:38.110 --> 25:39.750
But ultimately,
clothing is all about design,

25:39.750 --> 25:41.070
right? We...

25:43.440 --> 25:44.070
Okay.

25:45.120 --> 25:46.640
Alright, alright. Okay.

25:46.720 --> 25:47.270
Okay.

25:47.880 --> 25:48.400
Okay.

25:48.680 --> 25:50.140
I'll wait to hear from you.

25:50.240 --> 25:50.900
Okay, okay.

25:55.640 --> 25:56.770
You can still laugh?

25:57.070 --> 25:57.750
You have no idea

25:57.750 --> 25:58.510
how snobbish the media is

25:58.510 --> 25:59.480
these days.

25:59.750 --> 26:01.700
The interview we scheduled
has to be postponed.

26:01.700 --> 26:03.160
And the 10 inside pages we secured

26:03.160 --> 26:04.040
are being cut down too.

26:04.040 --> 26:04.650
And now,

26:04.680 --> 26:05.830
Editor-in-Chief Cui just called again,

26:05.830 --> 26:06.830
and the cover we were promised

26:06.830 --> 26:07.960
is no longer guaranteed.

26:07.960 --> 26:08.590
They want to wait and see

26:08.590 --> 26:10.680
how Elegance's Fashion Show turns out.

26:10.680 --> 26:11.740
Let them wait then.

26:12.070 --> 26:12.750
By the end of it,

26:12.750 --> 26:14.680
who knows who will be begging whom?

26:18.440 --> 26:21.100
You don't think
their fashion show will be good?

26:21.350 --> 26:22.440
Who said that?

26:23.270 --> 26:24.070
Ji Ya has spent so many years

26:24.070 --> 26:25.160
in the U.S.—

26:25.310 --> 26:27.110
she's seen things we haven't.

26:27.400 --> 26:28.960
As long as she doesn't go overboard,

26:28.960 --> 26:30.440
the show will definitely be impressive.

26:30.440 --> 26:31.700
Then we're in trouble.

26:31.750 --> 26:32.980
Even you said so yourself—

26:32.980 --> 26:35.110
we'd better think of
a backup plan quickly.

26:35.110 --> 26:35.750
Um...

26:35.960 --> 26:37.510
if your magazine idea fails,

26:37.510 --> 26:38.550
do you have a backup plan?

26:38.550 --> 26:39.550
Right, the commercial.

26:39.550 --> 26:40.750
What did the TV station say?

26:40.750 --> 26:42.030
If they can't air it,
I'll contact the Longcheng

26:42.030 --> 26:43.640
-and Shengcheng TV stations.
- Stop!

26:43.640 --> 26:44.640
No matter how much airtime we secure
in Shengcheng,

26:44.640 --> 26:46.160
only people in Shengcheng will see it.

26:46.160 --> 26:47.550
Luna's goal is

26:47.550 --> 26:49.210
to expand across the country.

26:50.680 --> 26:52.030
Yes, I know that.

26:52.030 --> 26:53.640
But aren't we short on funds?

26:53.640 --> 26:55.240
It's gonna cost one million.

26:56.530 --> 26:57.240
I'm starting to regret

26:57.240 --> 26:59.400
having given Lin Meijuan that much money.

26:59.400 --> 27:01.070
I should've paid in installments.

27:01.070 --> 27:01.830
That way, I'd have

27:01.830 --> 27:03.030
more cash on hand now.

27:03.640 --> 27:04.440
Chen,

27:05.000 --> 27:06.110
most men would

27:06.110 --> 27:07.110
probably regret

27:07.110 --> 27:08.880
giving so much to their ex-wife.

27:08.880 --> 27:09.680
But you—

27:09.920 --> 27:11.720
you just wish you'd paid in installments.

27:11.720 --> 27:12.850
You're a decent guy.

27:13.070 --> 27:13.870
A good person.

27:14.310 --> 27:15.510
You deserve someone better.

27:15.510 --> 27:17.970
Flattering me right now
isn't going to help.

27:18.030 --> 27:18.480
Well,

27:18.540 --> 27:19.200
so, right now,

27:19.200 --> 27:20.730
how much are we still short?

27:21.160 --> 27:22.450
If needed, I'll sell this.

27:22.450 --> 27:24.310
I know it won't be enough, but still...

27:24.310 --> 27:25.550
Chen, rest assured.

27:25.550 --> 27:27.310
The ad will get through just fine.

27:27.310 --> 27:29.880
But given the current situation,

27:30.030 --> 27:32.760
we might need to
release it earlier than planned.

27:32.880 --> 27:33.810
What do you mean?

27:34.000 --> 27:34.550
Look,

27:34.750 --> 27:36.010
you have to understand

27:36.310 --> 27:37.160
Ji Ya has

27:37.160 --> 27:38.400
American investors backing her.

27:38.400 --> 27:39.600
It's going to be huge.

27:39.720 --> 27:41.590
I heard her fashion show

27:41.830 --> 27:43.240
will be held at

27:43.270 --> 27:44.250
Louvre Square.

27:44.340 --> 27:45.590
By then, everyone will flock there,

27:45.590 --> 27:46.590
and who will pay attention to us?

27:46.590 --> 27:47.270
Really?

27:48.310 --> 27:49.270
That's great.

27:50.160 --> 27:50.830
"Great"?

27:52.790 --> 27:53.750
My goddess, Ms. Xia!

27:53.750 --> 27:54.510
I cannot follow a single word

27:54.510 --> 27:56.000
you're saying today!

27:56.720 --> 27:58.070
She may be the one building the stage,

27:58.070 --> 27:58.680
but the one performing on it

27:58.680 --> 27:59.940
doesn't have to be her.

28:00.240 --> 28:01.030
What do you mean?

28:01.030 --> 28:01.830
You want to go?

28:02.240 --> 28:03.270
But invitations aren't

28:03.270 --> 28:04.200
that easy to get.

28:04.400 --> 28:05.530
How will you attend?

28:05.590 --> 28:07.480
Given Ms. Ji Ya's personality,

28:07.590 --> 28:08.550
I bet she...

28:09.640 --> 28:12.100
Mr. Chen, Ms. Xia,
someone is here to see you.

28:13.200 --> 28:14.440
Good day, Mr. Chen, Ms. Xia.

28:14.440 --> 28:15.350
I'm from Elegance,

28:15.350 --> 28:16.610
Ms. Ji Ya's assistant.

28:16.920 --> 28:18.960
Elegance is holding a fashion show,

28:19.310 --> 28:20.920
and Ms. Ji has sent me
to deliver invitations

28:20.920 --> 28:21.830
to you.

28:22.400 --> 28:23.350
Ms. Ji said

28:23.550 --> 28:24.920
she very much wanted to invite

28:24.920 --> 28:26.160
everyone from Luna,

28:26.510 --> 28:28.480
but unfortunately, seats are limited.

28:28.480 --> 28:30.350
Aren't you two partners of the company?

28:30.350 --> 28:31.270
Here are

28:31.270 --> 28:32.530
two invitations for you—

28:32.530 --> 28:34.100
the best seats in the house.

28:35.550 --> 28:36.790
Ms. Ji also said

28:36.790 --> 28:37.960
that she sincerely invites

28:37.960 --> 28:39.130
her peers in the business from Luna

28:39.130 --> 28:41.440
to come witness what true fashion is.

28:43.000 --> 28:44.590
Please thank Ms. Ji for us.

28:45.060 --> 28:45.920
I'll take my leave.

28:45.920 --> 28:46.640
Thank you.

28:47.200 --> 28:48.000
This way.

28:49.550 --> 28:51.150
See? We got the invitations.

28:52.410 --> 28:53.550
[Elegance Fashion Show;
Exclusive VIP Access]

28:55.880 --> 28:56.640
Xia,

28:57.200 --> 28:59.730
did you study fortune-telling
or something?

29:00.070 --> 29:01.240
You called it.

29:14.480 --> 29:15.440
Fashion show?

29:16.030 --> 29:17.290
What is a fashion show?

29:18.000 --> 29:18.790
No idea.

29:20.370 --> 29:21.550
Never heard of it

29:21.550 --> 29:22.590
before.

29:23.590 --> 29:24.790
I heard these tickets

29:24.810 --> 29:26.340
cost several hundred each!

29:27.440 --> 29:28.370
That expensive?

29:28.480 --> 29:30.000
There are even scalpers reselling them!

29:30.000 --> 29:30.920
No way.

29:31.590 --> 29:32.400
Let's go. Let's go.

29:32.400 --> 29:33.800
This isn't a place for us.

29:33.880 --> 29:34.440
Let's go.

29:37.510 --> 29:39.650
[Fashion Show]

29:45.110 --> 29:45.640
Wang,

29:46.000 --> 29:47.480
don't just focus on the pretty girls.

29:47.480 --> 29:48.760
Take some shots of the venue too.

29:48.760 --> 29:49.820
Editor-in-Chief,

29:50.310 --> 29:51.310
I heard designers

29:51.310 --> 29:52.720
from Gangdao, Japan,

29:52.880 --> 29:54.200
and even the U.S.

29:54.200 --> 29:54.960
are here.

29:55.830 --> 29:57.360
Ji Ya really pulled a crowd.

29:57.640 --> 29:59.030
She's been in the U.S. for years,

29:59.030 --> 30:00.680
and with American investors backing her,

30:00.680 --> 30:02.240
it's no surprise she has resources.

30:02.240 --> 30:03.840
She really has money to burn.

30:04.070 --> 30:05.200
In comparison,

30:05.680 --> 30:06.720
Chen Xiliang

30:06.950 --> 30:08.030
is so outdated.

30:08.310 --> 30:10.170
So what if he opened stores first?

30:10.790 --> 30:11.960
In the end, he has to watch

30:11.960 --> 30:13.310
others steal the spotlight.

30:13.310 --> 30:14.370
Focus on your work.

30:14.440 --> 30:16.570
Don't jump to conclusions so quickly.

30:22.410 --> 30:23.130
Remember—

30:23.250 --> 30:25.200
maintain order at the venue at all times.

30:25.200 --> 30:26.200
One ticket per person.

30:26.200 --> 30:26.800
By the way,

30:26.830 --> 30:27.440
tell the ushers

30:27.440 --> 30:29.030
to check the seat numbers carefully.

30:29.030 --> 30:29.790
At shows abroad,

30:29.790 --> 30:31.070
people often sit wherever they want.

30:31.070 --> 30:32.430
That will offend the VIPs.

30:32.430 --> 30:33.400
Okay, I'll go see to it.

30:33.400 --> 30:34.000
Go.

30:39.240 --> 30:39.750
So nice.

30:39.960 --> 30:40.480
Okay?

30:44.820 --> 30:45.680
The earrings don't work.

30:45.680 --> 30:46.280
Wear another pair.

30:46.280 --> 30:47.010
Okay, Ms. Ji.

30:48.200 --> 30:48.600
Ms. Ji,

30:48.610 --> 30:49.670
how do I look today?

30:49.880 --> 30:50.550
Excellent.

30:50.920 --> 30:51.520
Walk well.

30:51.580 --> 30:52.580
I'll be watching.

30:53.400 --> 30:54.110
Baby, look.

30:54.270 --> 30:55.400
With so many

30:55.400 --> 30:57.590
beautiful models here,

30:58.310 --> 30:59.110
but still,

30:59.110 --> 31:00.970
you're the most beautiful woman.

31:01.070 --> 31:01.640
This is not

31:01.640 --> 31:02.720
the right time,

31:02.720 --> 31:03.440
honey.

31:03.790 --> 31:05.070
You're worried about something?

31:05.070 --> 31:05.640
Listen,

31:05.880 --> 31:06.930
here, everyone

31:06.960 --> 31:07.680
is for you

31:07.920 --> 31:08.780
and your brand.

31:08.960 --> 31:09.830
And you're the first-ever designer

31:09.830 --> 31:11.680
to hold a show here.

31:12.030 --> 31:14.490
And it's gonna be a success,
I'm telling you.

31:14.870 --> 31:16.670
Thank you for your support.

31:17.750 --> 31:19.480
I love to support your dream

31:19.500 --> 31:20.230
and career.

31:20.680 --> 31:21.030
But

31:21.030 --> 31:22.400
if I support

31:22.430 --> 31:23.190
one more show like this,

31:23.190 --> 31:24.650
I think I'm gonna go broke.

31:25.200 --> 31:27.590
Can you say I'm spending too much?

31:28.310 --> 31:30.350
This is a business battle.

31:30.550 --> 31:31.880
I was just joking.

31:31.880 --> 31:32.310
Okay,

31:32.330 --> 31:32.900
enough.

31:34.000 --> 31:36.830
I'll need to have a look
at today's celebrity.

31:37.160 --> 31:38.880
Yes, boss. Let's go.

31:45.880 --> 31:46.750
Ms. Ji,

31:46.790 --> 31:47.850
congratulations!

31:47.990 --> 31:49.160
I didn't expect that in Shengcheng,

31:49.160 --> 31:50.440
someone could hold such an impressive

31:50.440 --> 31:51.240
fashion show.

31:51.440 --> 31:52.470
You know how it is—

31:52.500 --> 31:54.680
in Gangdao,
every inch of space costs a fortune.

31:54.680 --> 31:55.920
Trying to organize a big event

31:55.920 --> 31:57.040
is no easy feat!

31:57.110 --> 31:57.640
Alright.

31:58.000 --> 31:59.310
The run of show is finalized.

31:59.310 --> 32:00.400
Make sure nothing goes wrong later.

32:00.400 --> 32:01.920
No problem. Don't worry.

32:03.150 --> 32:03.680
Also,

32:04.000 --> 32:04.880
our Kelly

32:05.000 --> 32:07.000
will become the brand ambassador, right?

32:07.000 --> 32:08.130
How are you feeling?

32:08.790 --> 32:09.960
I'm more excited now

32:09.960 --> 32:11.200
than on any stage I've ever been on.

32:11.200 --> 32:11.680
Ji Ya,

32:11.700 --> 32:13.640
thank you for giving me this opportunity.

32:13.640 --> 32:14.510
No need to thank me.

32:14.510 --> 32:15.510
You're the best.

32:16.030 --> 32:17.070
I'll be watching.

32:22.640 --> 32:24.370
Almost all the guests are here.

32:25.400 --> 32:26.600
They really all came.

32:30.250 --> 32:31.140
Who is that?

32:37.000 --> 32:37.960
Isn't that Teresa Li?

32:37.960 --> 32:38.960
She is beautiful.

32:38.960 --> 32:39.510
Really?

32:39.510 --> 32:40.660
It really is Teresa Li.

32:40.660 --> 32:41.390
It really is!

32:41.750 --> 32:43.640
She looks even better in person
than in her films!

32:43.640 --> 32:44.480
Teresa Li!

32:47.400 --> 32:48.250
Teresa Li!

32:48.640 --> 32:49.840
Why is Teresa Li here?

32:50.000 --> 32:51.200
People from Luna are here too.

32:51.200 --> 32:52.160
Quick, go take some photos!

32:52.160 --> 32:52.920
Teresa Li!

32:53.750 --> 32:54.880
She's so beautiful!

32:54.880 --> 32:56.790
Our whole family loves her!

32:57.070 --> 32:57.990
Teresa Li!

33:01.350 --> 33:03.150
This place is set up pretty well.

33:03.310 --> 33:04.110
Yeah, not bad.

33:05.550 --> 33:06.680
Let's go take a look.

33:09.310 --> 33:10.130
Senior!

33:10.160 --> 33:11.510
It really is Teresa Li!

33:11.510 --> 33:12.240
Yeah.

33:12.640 --> 33:13.200
You look

33:13.200 --> 33:14.240
even better in person than in films!

33:14.240 --> 33:15.570
Teresa, look over here!

33:15.920 --> 33:16.590
Teresa!

33:16.590 --> 33:18.200
They're calling for Teresa Li?

33:18.200 --> 33:19.200
Who is Teresa Li?

33:19.590 --> 33:20.740
She's a film actress.

33:20.740 --> 33:21.740
An award-winner.

33:22.750 --> 33:23.880
A mainland actress?

33:25.550 --> 33:26.610
It doesn't matter.

33:26.880 --> 33:27.930
Today's star

33:28.030 --> 33:28.920
is Kaili!

33:29.880 --> 33:31.000
Xia Xiaolan

33:31.350 --> 33:33.030
gave the tickets to Chen Xiliang

33:33.030 --> 33:34.230
and another actress.

33:35.200 --> 33:36.710
Then, she got two tickets herself

33:36.710 --> 33:38.570
and sat on the side stage instead.

33:38.920 --> 33:40.720
What exactly is she trying to do?

33:41.270 --> 33:42.960
I'll have security
throw them out right now.

33:42.960 --> 33:43.550
No!

33:43.930 --> 33:44.750
If you kick them out,

33:44.750 --> 33:47.070
the papers and magazines
will run wild with speculation!

33:47.070 --> 33:48.200
No matter how successful

33:48.200 --> 33:49.200
our show is today,

33:49.440 --> 33:50.680
tomorrow's headlines will

33:50.680 --> 33:51.440
all be about

33:51.550 --> 33:53.310
why Teresa Li was kicked out.

33:54.480 --> 33:55.550
Don't worry.

33:56.400 --> 33:57.460
A mainland actress

33:57.540 --> 33:58.510
can't possibly match the popularity

33:58.510 --> 33:59.720
of our Kaili.

34:00.990 --> 34:02.310
But the boss of Luna

34:02.680 --> 34:03.640
actually managed to secure

34:03.640 --> 34:05.030
such good seats?

34:06.480 --> 34:08.080
I gave them the invitations.

34:11.440 --> 34:12.840
Ms. Ji, you really are...

34:12.960 --> 34:13.760
generous.

34:17.800 --> 34:18.360
Kaili,

34:18.710 --> 34:19.440
do your best.

34:19.880 --> 34:21.070
You're the only superstar

34:21.070 --> 34:21.960
of this show.

34:24.480 --> 34:25.840
Ms. Li! Ms. Li!

34:27.070 --> 34:27.590
Teresa,

34:27.840 --> 34:29.510
your dress is absolutely gorgeous!

34:29.510 --> 34:30.690
Do you like this brand?

34:30.690 --> 34:31.500
This dress

34:31.530 --> 34:33.170
was provided by Luna.

34:33.550 --> 34:35.150
It's part of
their fall collection this year.

34:35.150 --> 34:35.760
Luna?

34:36.000 --> 34:37.730
Is the dress not from Elegance?

34:38.510 --> 34:39.440
It's Luna's.

34:40.920 --> 34:42.440
The commercial I filmed for Luna

34:42.440 --> 34:43.760
will be airing in the next few days.

34:43.760 --> 34:45.280
I hope you all support it.

34:46.460 --> 34:47.030
-Okay.
-Sure.

34:47.030 --> 34:47.800
She actually brought up another brand

34:47.800 --> 34:49.130
right here at our event.

34:49.550 --> 34:51.190
Has nobody taught her any manners,

34:51.190 --> 34:51.840
or did she come here specifically

34:51.840 --> 34:52.760
to sabotage us?

34:53.480 --> 34:54.150
Teresa,

34:54.480 --> 34:55.800
how much did Luna pay you

34:55.800 --> 34:56.760
for the ad?

34:57.000 --> 34:58.000
Yeah, can you give us

34:58.000 --> 34:58.670
a figure?

34:59.630 --> 35:00.490
Please tell us.

35:02.960 --> 35:03.840
Normally, ad fees

35:03.840 --> 35:05.320
can't be disclosed.

35:05.520 --> 35:06.400
The reporters are probably just

35:06.400 --> 35:07.360
teasing anyway.

35:07.650 --> 35:08.460
Then...

35:08.800 --> 35:09.930
I won't answer that.

35:10.960 --> 35:11.480
No,

35:11.840 --> 35:12.770
you must answer.

35:13.230 --> 35:14.190
Just use the standard response

35:14.190 --> 35:15.230
I gave you.

35:15.800 --> 35:17.460
Is it inconvenient to tell us?

35:20.360 --> 35:21.320
To be honest,

35:21.760 --> 35:24.090
I've never seen
that much money in my life.

35:24.180 --> 35:25.140
Luna paid me

35:25.510 --> 35:26.760
a full 10,000 yuan.

35:27.280 --> 35:29.030
-Ten thousand?
-Ten thousand yuan?

35:29.030 --> 35:31.430
Seeing that much money actually scared me.

35:31.440 --> 35:32.470
Just thinking about

35:32.470 --> 35:33.920
shooting a commercial for a few days

35:33.920 --> 35:35.360
and making that much money—

35:35.360 --> 35:37.280
I couldn't sleep at night.

35:38.480 --> 35:39.800
Isn't that just capitalism?

35:39.800 --> 35:40.510
Exactly!

35:40.510 --> 35:41.400
What do ordinary people like us

35:41.400 --> 35:42.000
earn in a month?

35:42.000 --> 35:43.150
Just a few dozen yuan.

35:43.150 --> 35:44.480
She gets 10,000 just like that!

35:44.480 --> 35:45.880
How much do I make in a month?

35:45.880 --> 35:47.360
Why should you make 10,000?

35:47.360 --> 35:49.840
-Yeah, exactly.
-Yeah.

35:50.550 --> 35:52.150
That's totally capitalism.

35:52.190 --> 35:53.190
Luna actually hired

35:53.190 --> 35:54.510
such a stupid actress.

35:54.800 --> 35:56.550
How could she reveal her pay publicly?

35:56.550 --> 35:57.760
I told you—

35:57.930 --> 35:59.190
she's just a small-time actress.

35:59.190 --> 36:00.590
Nothing to worry about.

36:02.230 --> 36:03.360
Why do you get to make 10,000?

36:03.360 --> 36:05.190
Serves you right that you can't sleep!

36:05.190 --> 36:07.200
Our country is still developing.

36:07.520 --> 36:08.450
Many people

36:08.480 --> 36:09.880
have only just managed to afford food.

36:09.880 --> 36:11.280
You wear such nice clothes

36:11.280 --> 36:12.540
and makeup for shoots,

36:12.670 --> 36:13.510
whereas farmers

36:13.510 --> 36:14.480
toil in tattered clothing

36:14.480 --> 36:15.440
all year,

36:15.950 --> 36:17.190
yet their whole family's income

36:17.190 --> 36:18.550
doesn't even come close to a fraction

36:18.550 --> 36:19.550
of what you earn from one ad!

36:19.550 --> 36:19.960
-Exactly.
-Yeah.

36:19.960 --> 36:20.670
Teresa Li,

36:20.670 --> 36:22.110
do you really think this is appropriate?

36:22.110 --> 36:23.400
You made your pay

36:23.400 --> 36:24.110
public.

36:24.280 --> 36:25.800
If all other actors follow suit,

36:25.800 --> 36:27.630
t-the impact would be terrible!

36:27.630 --> 36:28.280
Everyone,

36:28.440 --> 36:30.440
I'll go back and write

36:30.440 --> 36:31.760
a scathing exposé today!

36:31.760 --> 36:33.280
I never hide my identity.

36:33.280 --> 36:34.880
I am Liu Xuan, a reporter from

36:34.880 --> 36:35.520
Jingcheng Evening News!

36:35.520 --> 36:36.080
Yes!

36:44.980 --> 36:46.260
No, I...

36:46.960 --> 36:48.400
What a shot!

36:48.400 --> 36:49.550
I'm using this one!

36:49.800 --> 36:50.760
Yes, yes!

36:51.030 --> 36:51.800
Alright, that's enough!

36:51.800 --> 36:52.960
That's enough photos!

36:52.960 --> 36:54.400
You're all ganging up on her

36:54.400 --> 36:55.150
without knowing the full story!

36:55.150 --> 36:57.110
How could you just
bully a woman like that?

36:57.110 --> 36:58.550
If you have any questions,

36:58.550 --> 36:59.950
ask me. I'll answer them.

37:00.040 --> 37:01.560
-Who are you?
-Who are you?

37:02.500 --> 37:04.500
I'm Chen Xiliang, the owner of Luna.

37:04.800 --> 37:06.190
I'm the one who paid

37:06.190 --> 37:07.790
Teresa Li's commercial fee.

37:08.440 --> 37:09.230
Teresa Li is

37:09.230 --> 37:10.400
an excellent actress.

37:10.400 --> 37:12.110
She's starred in so many great works,

37:12.110 --> 37:13.840
and yet I only paid her 10,000 yuan.

37:13.840 --> 37:15.400
"Only 10,000"?

37:15.570 --> 37:16.810
Do you know

37:16.840 --> 37:18.460
those female stars from Gangdao

37:18.460 --> 37:20.500
demand 100,000 upfront?

37:20.840 --> 37:21.960
-A hundred thousand?
-A hundred thousand?

37:21.960 --> 37:22.960
Well... Oh my god.

37:22.960 --> 37:24.760
So, of course, I chose Teresa Li.

37:25.030 --> 37:25.670
Besides,

37:26.070 --> 37:27.440
after I paid her,

37:27.440 --> 37:28.150
she told me

37:28.280 --> 37:29.630
she couldn't even sleep at night

37:29.630 --> 37:30.890
receiving that money.

37:31.800 --> 37:32.630
She asked

37:32.850 --> 37:33.590
if she could use

37:33.590 --> 37:34.920
her 10,000 yuan fee

37:35.110 --> 37:37.550
to have us make a batch of
school uniforms.

37:38.670 --> 37:41.070
She said she would personally

37:41.110 --> 37:42.570
deliver them to children

37:42.670 --> 37:43.670
in rural schools.

37:44.320 --> 37:45.230
-She donated it?

37:45.230 --> 37:46.070
-She donated it?
-She really donated it?

37:46.070 --> 37:46.670
So,

37:47.000 --> 37:48.130
I feel very ashamed.

37:48.320 --> 37:49.550
Teresa Li was willing to

37:49.550 --> 37:51.070
donate her entire acting fee

37:51.070 --> 37:53.120
to children in rural elementary schools.

37:53.120 --> 37:54.560
As the owner of Luna,

37:54.840 --> 37:56.230
I'm not that noble.

37:56.480 --> 37:58.340
I don't have her generous spirit.

37:59.440 --> 38:00.110
As for Luna,

38:00.130 --> 38:00.860
although

38:01.680 --> 38:02.510
we're still a small,

38:02.510 --> 38:03.510
new brand

38:04.400 --> 38:05.960
relying on modest profits
and quick turnover,

38:05.960 --> 38:07.560
today I am making a decision:

38:07.800 --> 38:08.460
from now on,

38:08.550 --> 38:10.510
for every piece of clothing we sell,

38:10.510 --> 38:12.000
we'll donate one yuan

38:12.430 --> 38:14.760
-to children in rural schools.
-One yuan.

38:15.000 --> 38:15.710
Really?

38:16.070 --> 38:17.130
Well, listen to me.

38:17.440 --> 38:19.110
Since you're all here today,

38:19.280 --> 38:21.110
I'd like to ask all of you here
to be my witnesses.

38:21.110 --> 38:21.590
From now on,

38:21.590 --> 38:23.150
we also welcome you

38:23.340 --> 38:24.440
to help supervise us

38:24.440 --> 38:26.640
and keep this good deed going together.

38:28.590 --> 38:29.520
Is that for real?

38:29.720 --> 38:31.630
You said
that for every piece of clothing sold,

38:31.630 --> 38:32.570
you'd donate one yuan—

38:32.570 --> 38:33.650
do you mean it?

38:34.070 --> 38:35.730
Since I've said it here today,

38:35.840 --> 38:37.150
with all of you reporters present,

38:37.150 --> 38:38.360
I absolutely will not break my word.

38:38.360 --> 38:39.480
I mean what I say.

38:40.710 --> 38:42.040
First, grab attention;

38:42.480 --> 38:44.320
then provoke misunderstanding
and criticism;

38:44.320 --> 38:45.840
finally, have an unexpected turn

38:45.840 --> 38:47.040
and reveal the truth.

38:48.670 --> 38:49.550
Even TVB's high-society drama writers

38:49.550 --> 38:50.460
couldn't have pulled off

38:50.460 --> 38:51.720
something this slick!

38:52.110 --> 38:52.840
If I had known earlier,

38:52.840 --> 38:54.550
I should've asked her to leave just now!

38:54.550 --> 38:55.400
Didn't you say

38:55.400 --> 38:58.530
that would only make the media
pay more attention to her?

38:58.800 --> 38:59.480
Afterward,

38:59.480 --> 39:00.960
we could always manage the press

39:00.960 --> 39:03.820
and make sure
they don't write anything out of line.

39:06.360 --> 39:07.000
Kaili,

39:07.150 --> 39:08.190
don't worry.

39:08.360 --> 39:10.620
The stage will still be yours in a moment.

39:12.230 --> 39:13.230
Truly shameless.

39:13.320 --> 39:14.450
Just too shameless!

39:14.670 --> 39:16.600
Who came up with such a dirty trick?

39:17.670 --> 39:18.280
Alright,

39:18.670 --> 39:19.480
don't worry.

39:20.510 --> 39:21.360
Today

39:21.880 --> 39:22.760
is Elegance's

39:22.760 --> 39:24.090
most important moment.

39:24.160 --> 39:25.360
We just need to remember

39:25.360 --> 39:25.920
to walk out there

39:25.920 --> 39:27.230
and show our own style.

39:27.800 --> 39:28.750
Tell the host

39:28.960 --> 39:30.360
to turn the music up a bit.

39:30.670 --> 39:31.280
Okay.

39:39.400 --> 39:40.480
We're doing an interview here!

39:40.480 --> 39:42.000
Can you turn the music down?

39:42.000 --> 39:42.590
Yeah!

39:42.800 --> 39:43.600
Tell you what.

39:43.800 --> 39:45.330
Here are my business cards.

39:45.390 --> 39:46.540
Because in a moment,

39:46.590 --> 39:47.480
the show is about to start.

39:47.480 --> 39:47.960
Okay?

39:48.120 --> 39:49.290
Let's not disturb

39:49.320 --> 39:49.980
their show.

39:50.070 --> 39:51.710
-Here, give me one!
-I want one!

39:51.710 --> 39:53.550
-Me too!
-Me too!

39:54.280 --> 39:55.110
Call me!

39:55.400 --> 39:57.320
I'll answer all of your questions.

39:57.320 --> 39:57.880
Here.

41:28.360 --> 41:29.560
Ladies and gentlemen,

41:29.560 --> 41:31.110
please give a warm round of applause

41:31.110 --> 41:32.550
to welcome once again

41:32.570 --> 41:34.130
Ms. Ji Ya

41:34.680 --> 41:36.120
and the famous singer,

41:36.150 --> 41:37.840
Ms. Wu Kaili!

41:38.800 --> 41:40.280
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

41:41.000 --> 41:42.670
Hello everyone, I'm Ji Ya.

41:43.280 --> 41:44.630
Thank you all so much

41:44.630 --> 41:45.670
for coming today.

41:46.190 --> 41:46.760
Here,

41:46.780 --> 41:48.280
I'd also like to officially announce

41:48.280 --> 41:49.630
the launch of our brand,

41:49.630 --> 41:51.030
Elegance!

41:51.320 --> 41:52.510
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

41:58.600 --> 41:59.680
Next,

41:59.710 --> 42:01.320
our brand

42:01.320 --> 42:02.800
will be working more closely

42:02.800 --> 42:04.760
with Ms. Wu.

42:04.840 --> 42:05.570
For example,

42:05.920 --> 42:07.630
Ms. Wu will shoot

42:07.630 --> 42:08.960
many commercials for us

42:08.990 --> 42:09.520
and

42:09.550 --> 42:10.550
will serve as

42:10.550 --> 42:13.480
the official brand ambassador!

42:15.030 --> 42:16.230
-Great!
-Yeah.

42:17.110 --> 42:19.000
Ms. Wu Kaili, may I ask,

42:19.000 --> 42:20.760
what is your endorsement fee

42:20.760 --> 42:23.110
for representing Elegance?

42:23.590 --> 42:24.550
-Yeah!
-Please tell us!

42:24.550 --> 42:25.960
We'd like to know, too!

42:26.150 --> 42:27.050
That company paid 10,000.

42:27.050 --> 42:28.670
Did they pay you 100,000?

42:28.670 --> 42:29.800
-Please tell us.
-Please.
